me to jail, bitch.

53:33.260 --> 53:36.410
bad decision.

53:42.700 --> 53:45.320
Oh, my god.

53:46.670 --> 53:48.970
Patty...

53:49.360 --> 53:52.610
there are things far worse than death.

53:54.380 --> 53:57.420
Like living with lies.

53:58.320 --> 54:01.200
You know what you've done.

54:02.320 --> 54:05.900
Now you have a chance
to set things right.

54:07.580 --> 54:09.630
Ray...

54:09.650 --> 54:13.230
There are things far worse than death.

54:14.930 --> 54:17.750
Don't worry about dying, patty.

54:18.800 --> 54:23.210
Face your fear. Face yourself.

54:28.190 --> 54:30.730
go to ellen.

54:30.740 --> 54:35.110
The truth is waiting
for you in that room.

54:47.380 --> 54:49.530
Everything okay?

55:20.400 --> 55:23.300
Oh, jesus christ!

55:25.620 --> 55:26.940
Dave pell.

55:27.220 --> 55:29.080
My informant just shot patty hewes.

55:29.090 --> 55:31.390
Just get to the courthouse
and make the arrest.

55:31.400 --> 55:33.110
If I leave her here, she's gonna die.

55:33.130 --> 55:35.240
That's not our problem.

55:52.990 --> 55:55.390
Oh, shit.

56:07.030 --> 56:08.920
*****

56:08.930 --> 56:11.230
Don't talk; save your energy.

56:24.400 --> 56:27.060
The gps codes will be
allowed into evidence.

56:27.070 --> 56:29.480
Thank you, your honor.

56:31.290 --> 56:35.290
Ellen parsons, you're under arrest.

56:35.650 --> 56:36.660
For what?

56:36.690 --> 56:38.410
Bribing an officer of the court.

56:38.460 --> 56:40.900
There must be some misunderstanding.

56:40.910 --> 56:42.160
Let's go.

56:42.180 --> 56:45.030
Did patty hewes get to you?
You working for her now?

56:52.230 --> 56:54.230
U.S.Marshal. Please step
away from the prisoner.

56:54.240 --> 56:56.260
She's in my custody.

56:56.270 --> 56:58.590
- And now you're in ours.
- Who are you?

56:58.600 --> 57:01.170
Cynthia shayes, U.S.Attorney's office.

57:01.180 --> 57:04.940
Sir, step away from the
prisoner. You're under arrest.

57:11.280 --> 57:13.100
What is going on?

57:13.140 --> 57:16.390
Ellen parsons is going
to bribe that judge.

57:16.410 --> 57:18.690
She's acting on her own.

57:18.720 --> 57:19.770
Understood.

57:19.790 --> 57:23.100
Talk to the people you
know. Destroy her file.

57:23.110 --> 57:26.210
Get the fbi to disown her.
I want her arrested for it.

57:26.220 --> 57:28.610
Done.

57:29.270 --> 57:32.210
Can you identify either of those voices?

57:34.510 --> 57:36.530
One of them is dave pell.

57:36.570 --> 57:39.100
How do you know mr. Pell?

57:43.000 --> 57:46.180
Agent werner, we know this
investigation is corrupt.

57:46.240 --> 57:48.250
Patty set this all up?

57:48.540 --> 57:50.270
Yep.

57:50.320 --> 57:53.630
When she figured out what was
going on, she hired me back.

57:53.640 --> 57:56.580
My sister knows everything.

57:56.590 --> 58:00.240
The U.S.Attorney's office is
going to need a statement from you.

58:00.250 --> 58:02.140
Of course.

58:02.170 --> 58:04.570
Dave pell's going to jail.

58:04.580 --> 58:07.410
U.S.Marshals. You're under arrest.

58:07.950 --> 58:10.710
You want to go with him?

58:12.550 --> 58:14.860
I want to cut a deal.

58:14.880 --> 58:19.130
Patty also... got this from dave pell.

58:19.750 --> 58:20.900
What is it?

58:20.930 --> 58:25.620
Evidence against walter kendrick
and ultima national resources.

58:25.640 --> 58:28.240
Put your hands behind your
back. You're under arrest.

58:28.250 --> 58:30.770
Bullshit! For what?

58:31.990 --> 58:34.830
Thanks, tom.

58:48.630 --> 58:52.230
<i>***</i>

59:05.260 --> 59:07.270
How you feeling?

59:09.460 --> 59:14.410
Doctor says putting the mind in neutral
will help speed up the healing process.

59:15.050 --> 59:19.340
Yeah, right. How is that going for you?

59:23.800 --> 59:26.740
the epa has begun the
cleanup in west virginia.

59:29.100 --> 59:31.050
Good.

59:31.060 --> 59:33.160
Still no word from ellen?

59:34.430 --> 59:36.470
No.

59:36.500 --> 59:39.420
Well, I called the hotel--
she checked out weeks ago.

59:39.440 --> 59:41.940
Her cell phone's disconnected, and...

59:41.970 --> 59:44.820
all my e-mails have bounced back.

59:56.240 --> 59:59.180
Things with patty didn't exactly...

59:59.190 --> 01:00:02.480
turn out the way I
thought they would, but...

01:00:04.200 --> 01:00:08.710
I got what I needed from her. For now.

01:00:10.460 --> 01:00:15.040
What exactly did you say
to her in that hotel room?

01:00:19.920 --> 01:00:23.180
It just feels so good to let it all go.

01:00:24.160 --> 01:00:28.230
I met someone else. I hope that's okay.

01:00:29.480 --> 01:00:32.690
I think I'll stay out here for a while.

01:00:32.700 --> 01:00:35.680
So let me know when she calls.

01:00:36.090 --> 01:00:38.910
I don't think we're gonna see her again.

01:00:38.920 --> 01:00:41.580
I got a new job offer...

01:00:42.830 --> 01:00:46.430
and I think I'm gonna take it.

01:00:46.990 --> 01:00:49.830
So I'll let you know how it goes.

01:01:01.080 --> 01:01:05.240
She'll be back. Trust me.

